Each dot represents a certain element in the periodic table. 
First part of the flag = red element = (2, 2) = Be
Second part of the flag = yellow element = (8, 15) = Er
Third part of the flag = green element = (4, 13) = Ga
Fourth part of the flag = blue element = (4, 16) = Se
Fifth part of the flag = purple element = (3, 16) = S 

Flag: RC3-2017{beergases}

Special thanks to Greg Daneault for this challenge!!!
